<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[مكية، إحدى وعشرون]</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
